{"tid":1331131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"江旻憓世錦賽奪銅 將重登世界排名第一","createTime":"2019-07-18T23:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T02:18:00.000Z","uid":29218,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9f500b1740fb854e656a096087cc31e249d5010d","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:30:56.000Z","msg":"香港電台消息"},{"pid":"3c0cb11e862c1573998344e65c7544709e05ac27","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:32:07.000Z","msg":"本港女劍擊手江旻憓世錦賽摘銅 創造歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469161-20190719.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469161-20190719.htm&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDdqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=5f921531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469161-20190719.htm&h=91d79f93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469161-20190719.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5110e08eaa6da22c273ce3918dd998b88bd88a5e","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:33:02.000Z","msg":"香港劍擊代表江旻憓，在匈牙利布達佩斯舉行的劍擊世錦賽女子重劍項目，為港隊歷史性贏得銅牌。<br />\n<br />\n世界排名第三的江旻憓，四強鬥巴西的慕孝臣，雖然以11比15不敵對手，但在賽事不設季軍戰之下，贏得銅牌。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n江旻憓在賽後說很開心，又說最近香港有很多不高興的事，因此很想打好一點，將好消息帶給大家。</span>"},{"pid":"3f87cab68c036cfdb939bf58d982de7bace00623","tid":1331131,"uid":217108,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"3c0cb11e862c1573998344e65c7544709e05ac27","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:32:07.000Z","msg":"本港女劍擊手江旻憓世錦賽摘銅 創造歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469161-20190719.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469161-20190719.htm&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDdqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%