:"2019-07-19T00:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />旻憓bb加油"},{"pid":"509a66af2404f97ba8ec9f40b98f574fa81f90c7","tid":1331131,"uid":195904,"like":6,"dislike":18,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T01:12:57.000Z","msg":"同佢扑過<br />\n扑嗰陣面都紅撚晒 好撚大汗好撚正"},{"pid":"63e6561de589fd583054129b05c1bba4e2538073","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T01:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190719/large/1563486370_739b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563486370_739b.jpg&h=66945507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190719/large/1563486191_fb21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563486191_fb21.jpg&h=6e05edf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7a5a0e5c8c3fd90e3037dae4fc6693225d7aa2f","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"25歲的江旻憓（Vivian） 2014年曾殺入世錦賽八強，惟未能再進一步，替港隊實現「零的突破」，此後她的世錦賽征途受挫，連連失利，2015年她64強出局，2017年陣前更不幸重傷退賽，去年傷癒又爆冷於64強止步。今年她狀態大勇捲土重來，由64強起面對塞爾維亞、烏克蘭、愛沙尼亞及法國對手關關難過關關過，終晉級四強鎖定獎牌。<br />\n<br />\nVivian四強對手慕孝臣於劍壇戰績彪炳，現年33歲的她世界排名22，其生涯早年代表意大利參賽，曾隨隊奪世錦賽團體賽金牌，2010年則獲個人賽銅牌，她2014年起轉籍巴西，2016年奧運亦嘗八強滋味。兩人過去兩次對壘，最近一次已是2016年的大獎賽，其時Vivian以一分之微險勝，今仗戰況依然緊湊，經驗老到的慕孝臣開局即掌握節奏，一直領先，Vivian沉着應戰，及後發現其弱點即連番得分，兩節過後追平8:8。<br />\n<br />\n然而關鍵第三節，慕孝臣重處上風，她連得四分拉開至13:9，此時Vivian大勢已去，最終以11:15惜敗，功敗垂成。個人賽過後，周日Vivian會夥同隊友朱嘉望、佘繕妡和連翊希再戰團體賽。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190719/59839151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190719%2F59839151&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDdqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=4308fcc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190719%2F59839151&h=2905e5ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190719/59839151</a>"},{"pid":"2064baa6fac9ee98c4b1ec64309d61075c9a7fd6","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ef8cdd42a485431169b1a4b4e500476fc22035","tid":1331131,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5015c268e29b3a560eb1756a9d10d9c2799ba56","tid":1331131,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"#香港勁揪"},{"pid":"dc19fc17256b59fbaa97236a4d227591041b9a8f","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XhItuacJvGqr4odL_b0q3g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-Hk/homerun/jessica_995/2653aebfbf924e025c20fa15fd1337a0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXhItuacJvGqr4odL_b0q3g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-Hk%2Fhomerun%2Fjessica_995%2F2653aebfbf924e025c20fa15fd1337a0&h=6db36dff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c79eb63536feffcfc2ad8c29d43cc54e2656e12","tid":1331131,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fie.org/athletes/22439\" data-sr-url=\"https: